Actual VPS configuration :

Debian 10 - 1 vCore - 2 GB RAM - 40 GB NVME Storage

How to deploy the basic software

  Copy/past the bashscript at #############
  Run the script with sudo right
    
    bash xxxxx.sh
    
  The script will install all requiered software
  The script will setup the config user for git
  The script will create the right repostiry on the webserver
  The script will clone the github repo in it
  

Get ready to work

  Connect with user acess 
  Navigate to the project directory 
  cd /var/www/altarborn.com

You are now ready to work !
